      • getTotalInvocationsCount

        long getTotalInvocationsCount()
        This value denotes the total number of all invocations of the instrumented methods within the genuine execution tree. The reported execution tree has usually less elements than this value due to various reasons. Please, refer to the Flopsar documentation for more details.
        Returns:
        total number of invocations within the execution tree.
